{"tid":1893354,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"實測5款交通工具細菌量　電車污糟過小巴","createTime":"2020-02-23T08:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T04:38:21.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"582ad35e5eb69e539b1ec8166447cc11ec7f6773","tid":1893354,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200223/_2020022314142817279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200223%2F_2020022314142817279.jpg&h=12fde149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪姨用麵包抹扶手。影片截圖<br />\n<br />\n無論是扶手抑或座位，搭交通工具時不免用雙手觸摸不同地方。本港Youtuber雪姨參考美國一個麵包實驗，用麵包觸碰幾種常見交通工具的扶手，實測哪種交通工具最污糟。<br />\n<br />\n雪姨先後用麵包抹在小巴座位扶手、電車車頭扶手、巴士按鈴及座位扶手、地鐵扶手及的士車門把手共5種交通工具，然後把麵包放在密實袋中等7日。一開始雪姨以為的士最少菌，而巴士和地鐵就最多，不過結果就出乎意料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200223/_2020022314142995536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200223%2F_2020022314142995536.jpg&h=f71baf2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一名最乾淨：小巴👑<br />\n雪姨都非常驚訝小巴扶手居然最乾淨，同未有抹過任何交通工具的麵包對照組結果差不多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200223/_2020022314143049287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200223%2F_2020022314143049287.jpg&h=d51752a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二名：地鐵<br />\n日均乘客500萬的港鐵，擺放5日時麵包只有微微細菌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200223/_2020022314142915398.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200223%2F_2020022314142915398.jpg&h=7cad313f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三名：巴士<br />\n多人搭的巴士上榜亦是理所當然。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200223/_2020022314143123831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200223%2F_2020022314143123831.jpg&h=560b71d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第四名：的士<br />\n雪姨話原來的士司機好少會清潔車廂入面，所以車門內把手是高危。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200223/_2020022314143285955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200223%2F_2020022314143285955.jpg&h=f1d12377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第五名最污糟：電車👎<br />\n當時只有雪姨一行人和1位乘客，目測是最乾淨，但居然最多菌！<br />\n<br />\n同場加映手機細菌測試，抹過手機的麵包污糟程度不下巴士。<br />\n<br />\n不過有關的測試僅供參考，除了抹手外，市民切記要洗手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ew2NeJP1kRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dew2NeJP1kRI&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=60835bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ew2NeJP1kRI</a><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1707433/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-KOL%E5%AF%A6%E6%B8%AC5%E6%AC%BE%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E7%B4%B0%E8%8F%8C%E9%87%8F-%E9%9B%BB%E8%BB%8A%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F%E9%81%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1707433%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-KOL%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25B8%25AC5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%258F%258C%25E9%2587%258F-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E7%25B3%259F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=b3e8db1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1707433%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-KOL%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25B8%25AC5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%258F%258C%25E9%2587%258F-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E7%25B3%259F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4&h=f9a037b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1707433/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-KOL%E5%AF%A6%E6%B8%AC5%E6%AC%BE%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E7%B4%B0%E8%8F%8C%E9%87%8F-%E9%9B%BB%E8%BB%8A%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F%E9%81%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"a4ef0dca18515f4ea60c25173bde6040cbe95826","tid":1893354,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"小巴個司機要自己清潔"},{"pid":"eec9acdfd1ced1bf3c88fbc434eef431ee8f2b31","tid":1893354,"uid":8087,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"點解叮叮會係第一位？<br />\n黨鐵同的士塊包啲霉勁好多啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0522738f59eeda3e734a5a9bdef479e6b44fc70d","tid":1893354,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"免費penicillin"},{"pid":"5aabba20f439585b032b3e35fa21351ea4c7f11f","tid":1893354,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eec9acdfd1ced1bf3c88fbc434eef431ee8f2b31","tid":1893354,"uid":8087,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"點解叮叮會係第一位？<br />\n黨鐵同的士塊包啲霉勁好多啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bebcdf0bb48625e2facb446cda084ba46b4789c","tid":1893354,"uid":196552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"細菌定霉菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩樣唔同野黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f816ee65e6a362afe138dc721d4cd921e7f9a9a8","tid":1893354,"uid":82018,"like"